<li><a href="http://www.childhoodphonics.com" class="external text" title="http://www.childhoodphonics.com" rel="nofollow">Using Phonics</a> — Extensive phonics information for parents and educators.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.phonicsontheweb.com" class="external text" title="http://www.phonicsontheweb.com" rel="nofollow">Phonics on the Web</a> — Phonics rules including letter sounds, digraphs, r-controlled vowels, and more.</li>
<li><a href="http://call.canil.ca/english" class="external text" title="http://call.canil.ca/english" rel="nofollow">The Sounds of English</a> — Comprehensive lists of English words grouped by sound and spelling.</li>
